{"tid":2003505,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"銅芯抗疫口罩邊度製造？","createTime":"2020-05-06T00:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T09:39:29.000Z","uid":18142,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6fa5c5b9cb8d553ffe145d8b3a3ac5974cd1bdca","tid":2003505,"uid":18142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T00:46:11.000Z","msg":"睇左幾個網都係寫本地研發，冇講邊度製造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81c348e901483efe941e6f7a71c2e7efcf6daba","tid":2003505,"uid":18142,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T00:54:55.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】全民派發的可重用口罩，由香港紡織及成衣研發中心（HKRITA）負責研發，於本港及東南亞製造。中心行政總裁葛儀文昨日說，口罩的兩個銅質層可抑制細菌及病毒。有學者解釋，氧化銅和氧氣接觸後產生的活性氧分子，可破壞細菌和病毒的蛋白質或核糖核酸，令其失去活性。<br />\n<br />\n換濾芯可再用 按疫情再供應<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥公布口罩名稱為「銅芯抗疫口罩＋&trade;」；英文名稱為「CuMask+&trade;」。她說市民可稱其為「C u mask」，因為「Cu」是銅的化學符號，「亦可以將它演繹為『我很想見你』的口罩，因為是『see you』 mask」。<br />\n<br />\n葛儀文在記招上解釋，HKRITA於2017年開發技術，在口罩中加入「弱磁場」，但只能清洗20次。而現時供予市民的口罩，以表面兩層含銅質層抑制細菌及病毒，中層作過濾，清洗後可重用60次，更換濾芯後可再用，創科局表示會因應疫情發展，計劃再向市民供應濾芯。葛儀文說，口罩在港研發，於東南亞及本地製造；創科局常任秘書長蔡淑嫻稱沒有工序或部件於內地進行或生產。<br />\n<br />\n終於搵倒，但仍然有比人搵笨既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53e2e0f0bcb5d59ded8513566684f6b10513a04","tid":2003505,"uid":4186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T00:55:47.000Z","msg":"好似越南"},{"pid":"ae6a379803d3ad8fc61e39cdb2dd26d8e21b3e1e","tid":2003505,"uid":159913,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T00:59:57.000Z","msg":"用字好鬼偽科學feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a2f1c960a15119552ef4181f6ee8053c65a8cd","tid":2003505,"uid":165136,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T01:20:20.000Z","msg":"戴咗就see u on the other side"},{"pid":"682f77520461d6854452b24c6597fdda030fa4d7","tid":2003505,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T01:25:10.000Z","msg":"see u on the other world  ! Heaven or hell"},{"pid":"634ccbe5fa5bcbf7615a279b681d38ebde896feb","tid":2003505,"uid":37111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T02:03:05.000Z","msg":"CUM ASK"},{"pid":"b78a2685d1aed8ca5bb59ec0d079a1da82206ae7","tid":2003505,"uid":117286,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T02:09:07.000Z","msg":"CuO + O2 = ????"},{"pid":"2171b9ba734b755a18831bffa07e44f37f99ccf3","tid":2003505,"uid":15406,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b78a2685d1aed8ca5bb59ec0d079a1da82206ae7","tid":2003505,"uid":117286,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T02:09:07.000Z","msg":"CuO + O2 = ????"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T02:49:30.000Z","msg":"cu + o3<br />\n<br />\n臭氧殺菌<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">鳩up勿認真</span>"},{"pid":"8d13bbc1d73537966b08dd12c8ab75b993319c53","tid":2003505,"uid":239661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:02:49.000Z","msg":"CU MASK<br />\n暴大口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b90e7f0fbadff44b4138b3c23207d0337cdf7cc","tid":2003505,"uid":304856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:45:04.000Z","msg":"人地話「本地研發」，唔係「本地製造」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24503dcaa155d98be17e00ddfde303513e3d1b1","tid":2003505,"uid":38139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d13bbc1d73537966b08dd12c8ab75b993319c53","tid":2003505,"uid":239661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:02:49.000Z","msg":"CU MASK<br />\n暴大口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T04:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808433b0a713069d5882efec3525bf759